    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, peel and roughly chop&nbsp;the onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> and carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Heat</strong> a large, wide-based pan with a matching lid (preferably non-stick) with 1&nbsp;tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> vegetable oil over a high&nbsp;heat</p>\r\n<p><strong>Once</strong> hot, add the onions and carrots, cover and cook for 3-4 min until beginning to brown</p>",
