      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, peel and finely chop (or grate) the garlic</p>\r\n<p><strong>Chop</strong> the tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span> roughly</p>\r\n<p><strong>Separate </strong>the&nbsp;coriander leaves from the stalks, then chop both roughly</p>",
